<i>每当我看见圣经 便不由感激颤抖</i>

36
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:23,060
<i>and then I read about the part</i>
<i>每当我读到</i>

37
00:03:23,060 --> 00:03:26,230
<i>where a carpenter cleared the temple...</i>
<i>那木工清扫寺庙...</i>

38
00:03:30,770 --> 00:03:33,010
Hey,come on,hon.
快点  宝贝

39
