Wait,wait,wait. I forgot something.
等等 等一下 我忘了东西

40
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,340
Hold on a second,Anna!
等我一下 安娜

41
00:03:36,340 --> 00:03:37,580
Ralph,you have the venison?
拉尔夫 你拿上鹿肉了吗

42
00:03:37,580 --> 00:03:38,980
Yup.
拿了.

43
