Um,Danny's dad said he'd sell me their old car.
丹尼的爸爸说他要把他的旧车卖给我

52
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:07,840
I got half of what I need saved from the summer.
今年夏天我已经存够一半钱了

53
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,980
- I thought maybe you'd...- forget it.
- 我在想你能不能.... - 别想了

54
