to keep up with the mortgage.
就目前的状况看连还房贷都成问题

56
00:04:14,150 --> 00:04:17,450
Well,why don't you rent out grandpa's old apartment house?
为什么不把爷爷的老房子租出去呢

57
00:04:17,450 --> 00:04:20,020
Like I keep telling your mother,it's an old building,
我不是一直和你妈说那房子太旧了么

58
00:04:20,020 --> 00:04:22,020
and it'll cost a fortune to fix it up.
要修好它也得花一大笔钱

59
00:04:36,670 --> 00:04:39,340
Okay,okay.
来了来了

60
00:04:39,340 --> 00:04:41,010
They're here!
他们来了!

61
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:44,680
Hello.
你好啊!

62
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:47,050
Happy Thanksgiving. Happy Thanksgiving.
- 感恩节快乐!  - 感恩节快乐!

63
00:04:47,050 --> 00:04:48,680
Anna,wait until we're invited.
安娜 要等人家邀请你才可以进去,

64
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:50,420
Oh,for God's sake,Keller.Get the hell in here.
看在上帝的份上 凯勒 快点进来吧

65
00:04:50,420 --> 00:04:52,090
Aah!
啊!

66
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:56,820
Keller,you got the deer you shot?
凯勒 这鹿是你打来的么

67
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:58,560
This one's Ralph's.
这头是拉尔夫打的.

68
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,160
Well,you killed it,you take it into the kitchen.
既然是你打的 你就负责把它拿进厨房去

69
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,530
All right. Thank you.
- 好的. - 谢谢

70
00:05:01,530 --> 00:05:02,930
Happy Thanksgiving.
感恩节快乐

71
00:05:02,930 --> 00:05:04,160
- Happy Thanksgiving. - There he is.
- 感恩节快乐. - 他在这儿呢

72
00:05:04,170 --> 00:05:05,700
Thank you. Happy t-day.
谢谢.感恩节快乐

73
00:05:05,700 --> 00:05:09,540
All right.Joy. Joy,three times.
好了 乔伊 乔伊 都跟你说过三次了

74
00:05:09,540 --> 00:05:12,540
Joy,get your dolls off the table.Y'all missing the game.
- 乔伊 把你的娃娃们从桌上拿走 - 你们都错过游戏了

75
00:05:12,540 --> 00:05:14,410
- Anna! Anna! - Hi. How are you?
- 安娜 安娜! - 嗨 你好吗?

76
00:05:14,410 --> 00:05:15,880
Hey. Happy Thanksgiving.
嘿 . 感恩节快乐.

77
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:18,180
Anna,come here.
安娜 过来这里.

78
00:05:18,180 --> 00:05:20,580
We wait until we're invited.You understand?
我们要先得到别人的邀请才可以进去 懂了吗？

79
00:05:20,580 --> 00:05:23,580
You're in charge of this.
你来弄这个吧.

80
00:05:23,590 --> 00:05:26,190
Us veterinarians make lousy butchers.
我们兽医切起肉来还真不在行

81
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:27,520
No problem.
没问题

82
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:32,060
Can I go outside with joy?
我可以和乔伊去外边玩吗?

83
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:35,460
Uh,convince your brother to go with you,and you can.
你能拉上你哥哥陪你一起去就行.

84
00:05:35,460 --> 00:05:37,900
All right.
好了

85
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:39,270
And wear a hat,please.
记得戴上帽子

86
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:41,300
You're just getting over a cold.
你感冒才刚好

87
00:05:41,300 --> 00:05:42,900
Joy,you wear a hat,too.
乔伊 你也一样

88
00:05:42,900 --> 00:05:45,870
Did you feel bad for that deer
你打死那头鹿的时候...

89
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:47,640
when you shot it?
是不是觉得有点难过？

90
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:50,540
Do you feel bad for cows when you go into McDonald's?
你去麦当劳的时候也为那些牛感到难过么？

91
00:05:50,550 --> 00:05:52,480
That's... that's what my dad says.
我爸就是那么跟我说的.

92
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,910
And the deer,if they have too many babies,
说到鹿嘛 如果它们生了太多小鹿

93
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,720
then the babies starve anyway.
那些小鹿最后也会饿死的

94
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:58,750
You gotta keep the population down.
所以你需要控制种群的数量

95
00:05:58,750 --> 00:06:01,490
Right. Your dad say that,too?
也对 这也是你爸和你说的么

96
00:06:01,490 --> 00:06:03,090
Pull harder.
用力拉.

97
00:06:03,090 --> 00:06:06,130
Hey,hey! Get away from that thing!
嘿 嘿! 离那辆车远一点!

98
00:06:06,130 --> 00:06:07,730
Let me see that.
让我来试试.

99
00:06:07,730 --> 00:06:08,900
Come on,let's go.
快点 我们走吧

100
00:06:08,900 --> 00:06:10,230
No.
不.

101
00:06:10,230 --> 00:06:12,130
I said let's go!
我说了 我们走！

102
00:06:12,130 --> 00:06:14,670
Stop. You can't just take somebody's stuff like that.
下来 你不能随便碰别人的东西

103
00:06:14,670 --> 00:06:15,970
No! Let's go!
不能上去 我们走吧!

104
00:06:15,970 --> 00:06:17,300
Come on. Come on,come on,come on.
听话 听话 快下来

105
00:06:18,570 --> 00:06:20,110
Wait. Shh.You hear that?
等等 嘘..你听到了吗?

106
00:06:22,080 --> 00:06:23,580
Somebody's in there.
有人在里面.

107
00:06:23,580 --> 00:06:25,450
All right,I don't feel like getting yelled at.
这下好了 我可不想被车主骂

108
00:06:25,450 --> 00:06:29,320
Let's go. Not on Thanksgiving,okay?
我们走吧 感恩节的时候别惹事 知道了吗

109
00:06:38,590 --> 00:06:40,360
Now the school board's telling me
现在 学校董事会告诉我说

110
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:42,360
there's no money for new marching-band uniforms.
他们没钱给军乐队买新制服

111
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:44,100
These kids are wearin' the same uniforms
我们去那里的时候

112
00:06:44,100 --> 00:06:46,200
they had when we went there,and they were old then.
那些孩子们还穿着原来的旧制服

113
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:48,200
I mean,marchin' right out of 1979.
和1979年那会一模一样

114
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:51,170
Why isn't he speaking to me?
为什么它不跟我说话

115
00:06:51,170 --> 00:06:52,970
He doesn't speak.
它不会说话

116
00:06:52,970 --> 00:06:54,810
Cutie pie.
可爱吧

117
00:06:54,810 --> 00:06:56,380
Mm-hmm.
嗯嗯.

118
00:06:56,380 --> 00:06:58,010
Oh,my gosh!
喔 天哪!

119
00:06:58,010 --> 00:06:59,810
He's fast,too.
它跑得可快了

120
00:06:59,810 --> 00:07:03,150
He's so quick.
Is that a slide?
太快了 那是个滑梯吗?

121
00:07:03,150 --> 00:07:06,120
Thank you,all. Thank you,all. Got a surprise.
谢谢大家 我要给你们个惊喜.

122
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:11,520
And I am taking requests.
我可以给你们来一个『听众点播』

123
00:07:11,530 --> 00:07:13,460
Yes! No.
- 好! - 别

124
00:07:15,700 --> 00:07:18,800
You gotta listen out for it,'cause this is not easy.
你们都得好好听听 这可不是件容易事

125
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:21,970
Mom. Mommy,can I take joy to our house?
妈妈 我可以带乔伊去我们家吗

126
00:07:21,970 --> 00:07:23,470
Why?
为什么呀

127
00:07:23,470 --> 00:07:25,740
My red whistle.She's gonna help me look for it.
她要去帮我找我的红口哨.

128
00:07:25,740 --> 00:07:28,140
Oh,my sweetheart,I think that red whistle is long gone.
噢 宝贝 那个口哨早就不见了呀

129
00:07:28,140 --> 00:07:29,640
What whistle?
什么口哨

130
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:31,710
The emergency whistle daddy gave me.
是我爸爸给我的求救口哨

131
00:07:31,710 --> 00:07:33,280
I lost it...
被我弄丢了...

132
00:07:35,350 --> 00:07:37,850
133 days ago.
...大约133天以前.

133
00:07:37,850 --> 00:07:40,490
Well,if you want to find a whistle,
好吧 如果你想找到它

134
00:07:40,490 --> 00:07:42,890
you have to whistle for it.
得也得先吹几声口哨

135
00:07:42,890 --> 00:07:44,760
So we'll do "jingle bells" to find it.
所以 我们先来表演一首『铃儿响叮当』吧 好不好

136
00:07:49,230 --> 00:07:53,330
<i>Jingle bells,Batman smells,Robin laid an egg</i>
<i>叮叮当 蝙蝠侠香 罗宾下蛋黄</i>

137
00:07:53,330 --> 00:07:57,670
